category.name: All Bosses
category.rules:
Playing on a clean file, defeat all main bosses (i.e. you don't have to beat all 9 of King Dice's "minibosses") on a single difficulty.

For Expert, you must use the Fresh Expert Glitch. See: [link](http://www.docs.google.com/document/d/1OEchIopd8IqfKu283U0rWYzN44mg-OJSR9pnlSp3UyE/edit#) (towards bottom of document under Glitches - Difficulty).

All of the game rules apply.

All competitive run submissions must contain in-game audio. Here are what we define as competitive for the following "All Bosses" categories:
- All Bosses Regular Legacy: below 26 minutes
- All Bosses Regular Current Patch: below 33 minutes
- All Bosses Simple Legacy: below 19 minutes
- All Bosses Simple Current Patch: below 24 minutes

If a category is not listed above, all "All Bosses" runs will be accepted without in-game audio for now unless they classify as World Record.
